  "6-72": (
    caption: [Location of the protein components of the bacterial large ribosomal subunit. The rRNAs (5S and 23S) are shown in blue and the proteins of the large subunit in green. This view is toward the backside of the ribosome relative to Figure 6–66A; the interface with the small subunit is facing into the page. (PDB code: 1FFK.)],
    path: "../fig/image_place_holder.png"
